para_trans: On setting up of Rama Care Centre.
Government Decision No: Ramake. 2023 / P.No.267 / Health-3
10th Floor, Gokuldas Tejpal Hospital Complex Building,
Read: Letter from Health Services Commissionerate, Mumbai No. By / Room-3T-5 / TCU
A proposal to set up a 20-bed Rama Care Centre at the 100-bed Sub-District Hospital, Yevla District Nashik was under consideration of the government.

Separate action will be taken regarding the acquisition of space for the Rama Care Centre of beds and the construction and creation of posts in the prescribed manner.
